Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:30.35,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}M.I.N.A.M.I.K.E Let's Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:36.95,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,310)}一年之計好像在於元旦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:03.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(300,380)\frz19}壓\N歲\N錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:03.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(720,230)\frz19}壓\N歲\N錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶賀新年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年會鼓動起幹勁加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點進行表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我拿起這把傘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用它把二宮同學轉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將被轉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田要幾個年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了新年參拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了壓歲錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了風箏轉了陀螺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可內田還是依然每天來我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的年糕湯你吃了兩塊年糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個一組是常識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二貫壽司放一碟也是同樣的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回轉壽司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  你知道貫這個單位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田在別人家裏吃了一堆年糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田把紅豆湯都喝得一乾二淨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夏天拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這個是夏天時內田的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在會變成怎麼樣的慘狀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太誇張了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那明天去溫水泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果年末年初沒有過著慵懶的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會有問題的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來泳池  到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈突然要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈總是很突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  趁這個機會為了夏天來練習游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  來幫我下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  夏奈  放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  這個肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是年糕太好吃的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成什麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經當不了新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來到泳池卻沒什麼可以做的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是為了這個才來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來還想弄個特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓內田那不像樣的肚子瘦下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那肚子是何等不堪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  又不是那麼嚴重的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須趁現在縮回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  要採取地獄溫水減肥特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像有了幹勁的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然接受過游泳的特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還沒有特訓過別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想特訓別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就叫我魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算叫你魔鬼教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年的泳池教學中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怨你的一不留神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以來特訓啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是復仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披著特訓皮的復仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯之後再特訓怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來這裏的食堂做出來的東西似乎很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋也很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的冰淇淋是最棒的享受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  去吃午飯吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧春香的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下回把圭子她們也叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天為什麼沒有叫她們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不是去旅行就是回老家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天一夜的南家旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下…下回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的肚子才是最需要特訓的啊  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是千秋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼既然肚子也飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼教官  先睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼教官盡情享受慵懶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別大喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是覺得比想像中的小一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是特別的漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊兩個人在寒假的時候去海外旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像去看了什麼有名的建築
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  我也想去海外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子寒假的時候去了哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去了奶奶家那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶家似乎很遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都相當遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是京都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  夏奈  特別大的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個建築叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪你究竟去了哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子呢  去了哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？喂  圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在考慮什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  三學期開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就是馬拉松大會了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到這個就鬱悶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  馬拉松大會要跑多遠來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是6英里左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:57.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1英里＝1.6千米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  我以為是26英里左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說英里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過趁現在開始訓練就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看春天還有體檢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始減肥的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假的時候重了4磅左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:12.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1磅約＝453.6克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不注意的話就會超過100磅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說為什麼是磅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說千米千克之類的不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是維持著海外心情可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是海外心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  海外組的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子的京都心情還沒有散去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子和往常一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有馬拉松和體檢真是鬱悶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被傳染了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了  事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我藤岡  大家都去京都了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬拉松是要跑多少公里來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是10公里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  我還以為是42.195公里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是全長馬拉松啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩步調好一致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  跑馬拉松又能讓人瘦多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是每日堅持就不會瘦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跑10公里體重就能減2公斤就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說馬拉松大賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的  因為就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡同學的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  藤岡同學你是不是有點曬黑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放假時有去哪裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？能看的出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前被帶著去單板滑雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點被雪反射的太陽光曬黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曬痕像鬍子一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很會滑雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦  也就還行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  大家都從京都回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是回來了  剛才有一瞬間變回了正常的腔調
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈說話好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.00,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}終於要對決了！！魔王篇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:16.98,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}危險！勇者篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是火鍋好啊  吃火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鍋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為冷就提議吃火鍋也太不動腦子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯那就吃火鍋吧  做起來還方便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是要吃火鍋啊  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種大冷天吃火鍋最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  春香  一起去外面玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下大雪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你們不知道積雪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為知道才在被爐裏懶洋洋的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先從被爐裏出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  別看我這樣  我也是很怕冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從被爐爬出來是需要事先做心理準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香在寫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  夏奈  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出門的話就拜託你順便買點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來春香是肯定不打算出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  我還是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  被爐取暖什麼的  忙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也拜託千秋去買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多積雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  幹嘛攢雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有雪  那當然是先打雪仗再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是骨子裏就喜歡胡鬧的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是要大家一起決定玩什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看它這樣  它是個飯團哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃  扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你們是要打雪仗嗎  打雪仗對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊  那就來戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你們都收拾掉  戰吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  是很有力氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  也看棒球比賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是壘球的扔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  也是喜歡足球的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真下手了啊  看我這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次投犯規球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學生對中學生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  只有我是中學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一球！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我是這幅慘狀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是小學生對中學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不公平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且別看我這樣  其實都還沒有輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快認輸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香也是來打雪仗的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘帶錢包了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他要買的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(540,300)\frz-27}鬼\N面\N具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(800,360)\frz-27}節\N分\N的\N豆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都走到這了  幹嘛不自己去買
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  我還是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要回被爐裏去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原句是节分撒豆子时说的「鬼は外」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節分？節分是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍不知道什麼是節分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  節分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的來說  就是在家裏撒豆子把惡鬼給趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再把福請進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:17:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的萬聖節也是  最近節日都好高雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節分從很久以前就有了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我來扮演鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  一邊說「鬼快出去」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊把這些豆撒在鬼身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼快出去  鬼快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要打敗我的話  就準備一億顆豆子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常人家裏怎麼可能有一億顆豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是豆子也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟熊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福快來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿一億顆出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被撒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不是說了撒豆子要適度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾乾淨之後來吃點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼也在收拾豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家特製  惠方蛋糕卷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節分真是個好東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一塊不夠  再來一塊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說鬼可以隨便撒嬌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是鬼嘛  撒嬌有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  面具借我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再給我一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋也再來一塊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鬼也能拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那我去準備晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  你打算在家裏待到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼是要出去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道說  身為鬼的我要被趕走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…能幫忙的鬼留下來倒也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那鬼  幫我續一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  幫我揉揉肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會使喚鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  不想喝咖啡了幫我買瓶果汁回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是鬼吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幹了！待遇太差幹不下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  鬼要是被小看了就玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我來告訴你什麼是真正的鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鬼  果汁還沒買來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去買吧  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫我揉肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己揉去  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去打掃浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天輪到你打掃吧  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是平時的千秋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去給春香姐姐幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了那只是平時的千秋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  千秋  這個拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要放胡蘿蔔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
